author: NPR Music
description:
The award-winning Broadway musical Death Becomes Her left behind some special objects at the Desk. NPR Music’s resident theatre nerd, Mitra Arthur, tells us the story behind them.

Host: Mitra Arthur/NPR
Producers: Sofia Seidel/NPR & Kara Frame/NPR
